page.title: 05Keynsham High Street.
page.content: Keynsham is a very busy and crowded town but in some places it is quite peaceful. The busiest streets are the High Street and Temple Street.They join together to make one long shopp- ing centre. The High Street is still very busy even though the by-pass was built. All day long cars,lorries and motor-bikes go by. Lots of people use the High Street because there are lots of different shops to go to, but you cannot get around quickly because there are so many people. The Town Hall is like a tower. You can see for miles. On the patio outside you can sometimes see paintings by artists. Next door to the Town Hall is the library. The Fire Station is by the Leisure Centre on Temple Street. Gate- way Supermarket has had two fires this year. They caused a lot of damage. The second time they caught a teenager.
